{Thrash}

    The shark had ignored the threat and grinned as the maximal had turned
tail after his friend, giving chase Thrash found it easy to follow the bot
watching as the group struggled over the fem bot, his toothy maw grinning
evilly he opened it up and let loose, the whistle of drunk missiles drowned
out the conversations as a barrage of 8 wildly flying missiles rocketed
towards the struggle, two of which hit near by trees sending them crashing
out of the way...

    Maximal, Predicon, whatever. Thrash didn't care who these bots were, he
didn't need 25 ways to kill a bot...one would do...Utterly.
